1、Login reward is based in one month cycle and %s USDP power for 1 day login. 
2、Login for 3 consecutive days to receive a additional reward of %s USDP power; 
3、Login for 7 consecutive days to receive a additional reward of %s USDP power; 
4、Login for 15 consecutive days to receive a additional reward of %s USDP power; 
5、Login for 28 consecutive days to receive a additional reward of %s USDP power; 
6、The rewarded USDP power can mine USDP tokens. With more USDP power, users can get more mining rewards.
